definition:
A man living at the time of United Monarchy, only mentioned at 2Sa.21.16; 
 son of: Rapha (H7497A); 
 brother of: Goliath (H1555), Saph (H5593), Lahmi (H3902) and huge_man (H4060A) 
 § Ishbi-benob = "his dwelling is in Nob"
 son of Rapha, one of the nation of Philistine giants who attacked David in battle and was slain by Abishai
